// ASSERT: scan   -v, --version                 Print the version number, then exit.
// ASSERT: scan   -h, --help                    Show this help message, then exit.
// ASSERT: scan   -r ROOT, --root=ROOT          The root directories of your source files, defaults to '.', the current directory.
