// ASSERT: scan   -o OUTPUT, --output=OUTPUT    The output directories of html reports, defaults to '.', the current directory.
// ASSERT: scan   -b, --branches                Report the branch coverage. (It is an experimental feature and may generate imprecise branch coverage.)
// ASSERT: scan   --verbose                     Print some detail messages, including parsing data for the gcov file.
// ASSERT: scan   --html-details                Generate html reports for each source file.
// ASSERT: scan   -k, --keep                    Keep gcov files after processing.
// ASSERT: scan   -s SOURCE, --source=SOURCE    The directories of cangjie source files.
// ASSERT: scan   -e EXCLUDE, --exclude=EXCLUDE
// ASSERT: scan                                 The cangjie source files starts with EXCLUDE will not be showed in coverage reports.
